data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER, ACCEPTING ALL OFFERS! This METICULOUSLY MAINTAINED, single story home sits on a ONE ACRE LOT and is better than new with a newly installed FENCE and backyard SHED! Upon entry you are greeted with a stunning formal dining area directly across from the home office with French doors. Features include ceramic tile throughout the open concept living room, breakfast room and kitchen areas. The kitchen boasts an oversized island, perfect for entertaining, SS appliances, coffee bar, butler's pantry, and a walk in pantry. The living room has a beautiful floor to ceiling stone fireplace and an abundance of natural light flows throughout the home. The large game room can be used as media room, workout area, or additional home office! Enjoy the primary bedroom with it's large ensuite bath and backyard views! The backyard backs up to a gorgeous greenbelt that gives lots of additional privacy and there's still so much potential to make this your own. NO MUD!!
